tspan.tspan: As we move forward together, our union's strength lies in our shared
commitment to core values that guide every decision and action we
take. Grounded in Integrity, we ensure that honesty and ethics are at the
heart of all we do. We are Committed to Transparency, dedicated to open
communication and accountability, so every members voice is heard
and respected. And we are Driven by Diligence, working tirelessly to
achieve the best outcomes for everyone.

our collective resolve to build a stronger, more united future. If you
choose us to lead, we will fully embody these values, making decisions
that benefit every member and strengthen our union as a whole. We
believe in the power of our union to make a difference, and together, we
can continue to achieve great things.

Dont miss your chance to be a part of this crucial decision. Mark your
